<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_addform/addform">

    <div metal:fill-slot="extra_info" class="documentDescription">
      PLEASE BE EXTREMELY CAUTIOUS. This form creates a new "port" for the
      release of the distribution, to a particular architecture. Only admins
      should use it. It will have large consequences for the archive, and of
      course all mirrors. USE WITH CARE.
    </div>

  </div>

  <p>
    Once again, please make sure that you are certain you know what you are
    doing and why before pressing the button...
  </p>

</div>
    
</body>
</html>

